Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.92,0:24:36.31,Lucy-Song-English,,0,0,0,,There's a baby koala in the eucalyptus tree
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.60,0:24:40.98,Lucy-Song-English,,0,0,0,,Looking for its mother from branch to branch
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.23,0:24:45.68,Lucy-Song-English,,0,0,0,,It gathers plenty of leaves to eat
