Dialogue: 0,0:25:09.67,0:25:14.04,Lucy-Song-English,,0,0,0,,It's always so merry, so merry
Dialogue: 0,0:25:14.34,0:25:18.73,Lucy-Song-English,,0,0,0,,Uhahahaha wuhahahaha
