Dialogue: 0,0:25:23.77,0:25:28.77,Lucy-Song-English,,0,0,0,,I want to show you, I want to show you the forest animals
Dialogue: 0,0:25:29.02,0:25:33.97,Lucy-Song-English,,0,0,0,,I want to show them to you
